in Schulsystem ohne staatliches Bildungsmonopol beschreibt, oder dem der »Differenzierten Schule« als Darstellung der Folgen bisheriger Praxis - wird die Tragfähigkeit des Instruments diskutiert.  afunded by ÖFG  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Jan 2023) 0aSchool buildings. 4aAltbaumodernisierung. 4aArchitektur. 4aBildung. 4aBildungsforschung. 4aGebäudebestand. 4aTransition Theory. 7aARCHITECTURE / Urban & Land Use Planning.2bisacsh  aArchitecture.  aBuilding Stock.  aEducation.  aEducational Research.  aTransition Theory.2 aÖFGefunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2z978311069629508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Architecture and Design 2020z9783110704679oZDB-23-DAD08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2020z9783111025124oZDB-23-TGP0 cprintz978383764294040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839442944?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839442944423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839442944/original  a978-3-11-069629-5  DG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2b2020  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_AD  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DADb2020  aZDB-23-DGGb2020  aZDB-23-TGPb2020